<h1>莲</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">lián</span><span class=alesi>(lian2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 莲 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 莲</h2><div class=abo>
